		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Granted by </em><span style=\"font-family:Signika,\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika,\"><em>Jinya-Por for honoring them by swimming in the waters beside her shrine for at least ten minutes, for Jinya-Por was the Taumatan god of sailing, swimming, and the wind.</em></span></span></p><hr /><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika,\"><span style=\"font-family:Signika,\">For the duration of their stay on Bonmu, whenever you roll a success at an Athletics check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.c8TGiZ48ygoSPofx]{Swim}, you get a critical success instead.</span></span></p>",
